decoworld.model.world

Class MapProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.MapProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmptyMapProvider, IOMapProvider, NetworkMapProvider, RoomProvider

    public abstract class MapProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class that is extended to provide support for loading and saving Map objects through different methods (network, disk IO, magical ponies, etc).

      • provide

        public abstract Map provide(java.lang.String name)
        Provides a map, which is to be either loaded from disk/memory (server) or received over the network from a server (client).
        Parameters:
        name - the unique name of the Map to retrieve.
        Returns:
        a Map object corresponding to the provided name. Returns null on failure.
